  "prompt": "Where can I find a power outlet for my laptop at Melbourne Airport?",
  "response": "At Melbourne Airport, there are several locations where you can find power outlets for your laptop. Here are some options:\n\n1. **Terminal Lounges**: Both the domestic and international terminals have lounges that typically provide power outlets.\n\n2. **Gate Areas**: Many gate areas have power outlets available for passenger use. Look for seating areas where you can plug in your laptop.\n\n3. **Seating Areas**: There are specific seating areas throughout the terminals equipped with power points. \n\n4. **Business Facilities**: If you have access to business facilities or lounges, they usually offer power outlets and workstations.\n\n5. **Airport Services**: If you\u2019re having trouble finding a power outlet, you can ask airport staff for assistance.\n\nIt's advisable to arrive early and explore the terminal to find an available outlet. Enjoy your time at the airport!",
